</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[199,925,1158,1185]" pageId="13" pageNumber="370" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="13.[151,1437,150,1185]" box="[199,925,1158,1185]" pageId="13" pageNumber="370">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,328,1158,1184]" pageId="13" pageNumber="370">Etymology</emphasis>
. Named after the multiple striation on the forewings.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
